## ğŸŒ 1. What is Next.js?

**Next.js** is a **React framework** for building **server-side rendered (SSR)** and **static web applications**.

âœ… Built on top of **Node.js**
âœ… Uses **React** + **API routes** (backend-like endpoints)
âœ… Can serve both **frontend + backend in one project**

